            <title>[THRIFT-3463] Java can&apos;t be disabled in CMake build</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-3463</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If `-DWITH_JAVA=OFF` is given as argument to CMake it still tries to find Java and fails if not found.&lt;/p&gt;

